  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      All patients undergoing carotid endarterectomy in Shaare Zedek Medical Hospital, during about
      1 year, will be offered to participate.

      Retinal and choroidal structural changes will be assessed using swept-source OCT technology
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
