  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Carotid stenosis requiring surgical management

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Ocular conditions: media opacities precluding fundus visualization, bilateral no-light
             perception

          -  Ocular surgery within 6 months prior to endarterectomy
      </textblock>
